### FeedbackHotel API Test Requests

### Get all hotel feedbacks
GET https://localhost:7000/FeedbackHotel
Content-Type: application/json

### Get hotel feedback by ID
GET https://localhost:7000/FeedbackHotel/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get hotel feedbacks by user ID
GET https://localhost:7000/FeedbackHotel/user/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get hotel feedbacks by hotel ID
GET https://localhost:7000/FeedbackHotel/hotel/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get hotel feedbacks with filters
POST https://localhost:7000/FeedbackHotel/filter
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "hotelId": 1,
  "rating": 5,
  "fromDate": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "toDate": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "limit": 10,
  "offset": 0
}

### Create new hotel feedback
POST https://localhost:7000/FeedbackHotel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "hotelId": 1,
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Excellent hotel with great service and beautiful rooms!"
}

### Update hotel feedback
PUT https://localhost:7000/FeedbackHotel/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Good hotel but room service could be better."
}

### Delete hotel feedback
DELETE https://localhost:7000/FeedbackHotel/1
Content-Type: application/json

### Check if user can create feedback for hotel
GET https://localhost:7000/FeedbackHotel/can-create?userId=1&hotelId=1
Content-Type: application/json

### Create feedback with different ratings
POST https://localhost:7000/FeedbackHotel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "hotelId": 2,
  "rating": 3,
  "comment": "Average hotel, nothing special."
}

### Create feedback with minimum rating
POST https://localhost:7000/FeedbackHotel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 3,
  "hotelId": 3,
  "rating": 1,
  "comment": "Terrible experience, would not recommend."
}

### Create feedback with maximum rating
POST https://localhost:7000/FeedbackHotel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 4,
  "hotelId": 4,
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Perfect! Amazing location, friendly staff, and luxurious amenities."
}

### Filter feedbacks by rating only
POST https://localhost:7000/FeedbackHotel/filter
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "limit": 20,
  "offset": 0
}

### Filter feedbacks by date range
POST https://localhost:7000/FeedbackHotel/filter
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromDate": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "toDate": "2024-01-31T23:59:59Z",
  "limit": 50,
  "offset": 0
}
